no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs.description:
Description

This rule disallows mixed spaces and tabs for indentation.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs: "error"*/

function add(x, y) {
	  return x + y;
}

function main() {
	var x = 5,
	    y = 7;
}

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs: "error"*/

function add(x, y) {
	return x + y;
}

no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs.option:
This rule has a string option.

- "smart-tabs"allows mixed tabs and spaces when the spaces are used for alignment.

smart-tabs

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule with the"smart-tabs"option:

/*eslint no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs: ["error", "smart-tabs"]*/

function main() {
	var x = 5,
	    y = 7;
}
